OL,3,CCouple who lost their child on holiday
OL,4,Coffer warnings to other teenagers
OL,6,FWhile thousands of young people across
OL,7,FWales look forward to jetting off
OL,8,Fafter exam results, for parents it can
OL,9,Fbe a worrying time.
OL,11,FOne couple who lost their child in a
OL,12,Ftragedy overseas are raising awareness
OL,13,Ffor teenagers to stay safe while
OL,14,Fhaving fun in the sun.
OL,16,FJust this week a 19 year old British
OL,17,Ftourist died after falling from a
OL,18,Fsixth floor balcony in Ibiza, leaving
OL,19,Fher family devastated.
