OL,3,CCouple who lost their child on holiday
OL,4,Coffer warnings to other teenagers
OL,6,FThat feeling of devastation is one
OL,7,Fwith which John Channon from Rhoose in
OL,8,Fthe Vale of Glamorgan is all too
OL,9,Ffamiliar.
OL,11,FJohn's son Tom lost his life six year
OL,12,Fago, after falling while trying to
OL,13,Fmake his way back to his hotel in in
OL,14,FMagaluf.
OL,16,FThis time of year is a difficult one
OL,17,Ffor John and his family, especially
OL,18,Fwhen similar incidents are still
OL,19,Fhappening.
