OL,3,CCouple who lost their child on holiday
OL,4,Coffer warnings to other teenagers
OL,6,FJohn said: "Obviously we've been on
OL,7,Ffamily holidays before but naturally
OL,8,Fas a parent you do worry. We try to do
OL,9,Feverything that we could to make sure
OL,10,Fthe kids will be safe. But
OL,11,Funfortunately people aren't going to
OL,12,Fbe looking out for you and you really
OL,13,Fhave to do a lot yourself.
OL,15,FThis time of year is a difficult one
OL,16,Ffor John and his family, especially
OL,17,Fwhen similar incidents are still
OL,18,Fhappening.
