OL,3,CCouple who lost their child on holiday
OL,4,Coffer warnings to other teenagers
OL,6,F"I think it really fills us with
OL,7,Fsadness because you feel after what
OL,8,Fhappened to us, it shouldn't happening
OL,9,Fagain. It's something that you have to
OL,10,Ffind a way through and partly the way
OL,11,Fthrough us was to try and find
OL,12,Fsomething positive to come out of
OL,13,Fthis."
OL,15,FAnd that has come in the form of a
OL,16,Fsafety campaign in Tom's name - one
OL,17,Fdeveloped with his former school and
OL,18,Fshared with schools and colleges right
OL,19,Facross Wales.
