OL,6,F"It will make other people aware of
OL,7,Fpotential dangers and hazards and
OL,8,Fmaybe make them better prepared and
OL,9,Fplan better."
OL,11,FFor John, the safety of future young
OL,12,Ftravellers is what Tom's legacy is all
OL,13,Fabout.
OL,15,FBut what can be done to minimise the
OL,16,Frisk?
