OL,6,FSuzanne Cumpston is a travel agent
OL,7,Ffrom Sam Smith Travel. She said: "Make
OL,8,Fsure that you take a very good
OL,9,Finsurance policy out. Make sure that
OL,10,Fyou have a 24 hour emergency telephone
OL,11,Fnumber on that policy.
OL,13,FAnd also to give that telephone number
OL,14,Fto their parents and guardians back to
OL,15,Fthe UK."
